{
  "page": "Falchion",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>A <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">falchion</a> is a short, one-handed, broad bladed sword with a single edge. It is used primarily for hacking. It resembles a cleaver in appearance.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearances_in_the_Novels\">Appearances in the Novels</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Falchion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearances in the Novels\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Falchion.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7c/Falchion.jpg/200px-Falchion.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"106\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7c/Falchion.jpg/300px-Falchion.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7c/Falchion.jpg/400px-Falchion.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Falchion.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Falchion</div></div></div>\n<p>The falchion is <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Bolton\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ramsay Bolton\">Ramsay Bolton</a>'s weapon of choice.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Falchion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div cl